<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your RelayFlow Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      color: #111827;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      table-layout: fixed;
      background-color: #f8fbff;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0099ff 0%, #00c2ff 100%);
      padding: 30px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #0077cc;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .content p {
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .btn-container {
      margin: 35px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .btn-reset {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0099ff 0%, #007acc 100%);
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.25);
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 0 40px 40px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    }
    .expiry-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #727782;
      background: rgba(0, 153, 255, 0.04);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .link-fallback {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      word-break: break-all;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>RelayFlow Help</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Reset your password</h2>
        <p>Hello <strong><%= displayName %></strong>,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your RelayFlow account. Click the button below to choose a new password:</p>
        
        <div class="btn-container">
          <a href="<%= resetLink %>" target="_blank" class="btn-reset">Reset Password</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expiry-note">
          ⏰ <strong>Please note:</strong> This password reset link is valid for <strong>30 minutes</strong> only. If it expires, you will need to submit a new request.
        </div>
        
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email — your password will remain unchanged.</p>
        
        <div class="link-fallback">
          If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser: <br>
          <a href="<%= resetLink %>" style="color: #0077cc;"><%= resetLink %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> RelayFlow. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Vibrant & Secure Real-Time Messaging Platform.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
